  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271692</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_010_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ここが&lt;Red&gt;ユークリッド村&lt;White&gt;？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Is this place Euclid Village? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271808</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_010_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>う～ん、
ぼくの知ってる&lt;Red&gt;ユークリッド&lt;White&gt;は
もっと賑やかだったけド</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It looks like that. Though the Euclid Village
I knew was a lot more active. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271880</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_010_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>マジでここなのか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Are we really in the correct place? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271968</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_010_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>場所は間違ってないから、
たぶん……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I don't feel this is the wrong place, so... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272092</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_010_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>んじゃ、ちゃんと
来れたってことだな！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Then we're where we're supposed to be! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272092</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_010_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>よし、行こーぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ok, let's move! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272156</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_010_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルール！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kururu! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272264</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_010_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>行こうって、きみ、
&lt;Klarth&gt;さん家の場所、
知らないでしょ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You're telling us to go, but we don't even
know where Mister &lt;Klarth&gt;'s house is. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272356</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_010_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>んなのテキトーに探して、
見つかるって</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We'll just have to find it, then! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272444</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_010_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>村の人に
聞いてまわった方が
いいよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I think we should also ask the people
in the village for directions. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272584</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_010_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>じゃあ、それで</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Just leave it to me! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272692</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_010_013&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そんなに&lt;Dio&gt;、
嬉しいのかな？
その英雄？　に会うのが</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Doesn't &lt;Dio&gt; look a bit way too happy? Are we
going to meet with a Hero or something? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272788</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_010_014&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Dio&gt;は昔から、
そういうお話好きだったから</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Dio&gt; enjoys being in the past so much because
he wants to see the people from his storybooks. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272864</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_010_015&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そっか
……そうだよね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah, I guess that's true... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
